PrecisEnactment of an ORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (2002, No. 3, CARCROSS/TAGISH FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which (a) prohibits the staking of mineral claims or prospecting in specific areas in the Yukon until March 31, 2008, and (b) repeals an earlier Prohibition of Entry Order made on December 13, 2001.
